headline.print_headline: New Zealand's Carter to Miss Start of Rugby Championship
headline.main: New Zealand's Carter to Miss Start of Rugby Championship

lead_paragraph: New Zealand flyhalf Dan Carter will miss at least the first two matches of the Rugby Championship against Australia after injuring his leg in last weekend's Super Rugby final.
